#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kate.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Kate"
msgstr "Kate"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kate.appdata.xml:8
msgid "Advanced text editor"
msgstr "Editor avantiate de texto"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kate.appdata.xml:10
msgid ""
"Kate is a fast multi-document, multi-view text editor for programmers by "
"KDE. It features stuff like LSP (Language Server Protocol) support, "
"projects, multiple cursors and selections, git integration, folder wide "
"search, horizontal and vertical splits, vi mode, syntax highlighting for "
"300+ languages, built-in terminal, dynamic word wrap and much more. It is "
"available on Linux, BSD, Windows and MacOS."
msgstr ""
"Kate es un rapide editor multi-documento e multi-vista de texto per "
"programmatores per KDE. Il ha characteristicas como supporto de LSP(Language "
"Server Protocol), projectos, cursores multiple e selectiones, integration "
"con git, cerca per dossier, divisiones horizontal e vertical, modo de vi, "
"evidentiar de syntaxe per plus de 300 linguages, terminal incorporate,"
"inveloppar de parola e multe altere. Il es disponibile sur Linux, BSD, "
"Window e MacOS. "

